channel.title: Adding the server to the MSSC
channel.description: Hello, When i was going to add my server to the mopars server status checker.. I filled all the information, but it says : This server has allready been posted.. I've tryed to change IP a couppel of times.. I was working for like 9 hour ago.. :confused:
